snippet.title: Xmas Shooting - Scramble!! Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Xmas Shooting - Scramble, the latest cute'em'up by Orange Juice, is now available in English!

Help Aru save Christmas in this humoristic, action-packed shooter set in the universe of QP Shooting - Dangerous!!
